data.description: This beautiful home embodies true southern charm. A covered front porch beckons you step into this spacious and bright home, which includes a sizable foyer and open concept layout downstairs, perfect for large gatherings. Upstairs has a spacious owners retreat and a private bathroom and walkin closet. Three additional bedrooms and a full bathroom and laundry room are also located on the second floor of this home located in the gorgeous community of Twelve Oaks.
